      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOOKS (2) missed narrowly two back before going under in a photo finish as the race favourite here last time out. It's been a while between drinks, but he draws the inside now and should be up front from the outset. Can go one better this time around. NICCY'S AFFAIR (5) hasn't been far away recently, beaten 0.5L most recently over 1230m here. Out in trip today which is the query, but she has placed here previously. Rates highly on her recent form and if she can stretch it to 1600m, she'll be hard to fend off. GINGERS SISTER (8) won narrowly two back before a 1.9L defeat most recently over 1500m. Campbell hops back on board today and he's won 2/3 aboard the mare. Likely to be back in the run again, but can finish off strongly and get back to winning ways. SIR BEAR A LOT (7) got back to his best last start over 1500m and is not to be discounted. MAGIC MIKEY (4) can be in the finish coming back in trip.",
